{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "無憂夢囈", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "名為客房區的迷宮", "storyInfo": "在艾雅法拉的鼓勵下，初華終於決定離開小島，出發尋找祥子。祥子也終於到達了初華的住處，然而兩人卻陰錯陽差地錯過了。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當重複的事情做了無數次，人總會變得麻木，不再有任何感覺。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當重複的一天度過了無數遍，人便會陷入這個循環之中。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無從自覺，無法自拔。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像一個漫長的、無盡的、無解的夢一樣。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伴隨著山中羽獸的啼鳴，每天清晨從床上自然地甦醒。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若想睡個懶覺，也不會有人催促，把頭重新埋進被子裡就好。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收拾好被子和床鋪，在廚房簡單地做一頓早餐。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煎蛋、麵包、牛奶……"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想吃什麼、想喝什麼，全憑自己的心意。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個人坐在鋼琴旁，按下一個琴鍵，將未調的琴弦一點點調成正確的音調。不知過了多久，再調下一根琴弦。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等到調完最後一根琴弦，第一根琴弦的音調又變得不準。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，如此反覆。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "38_g21_skystarry_L1/38_g21_skystarry_R1/38_g21_skystarry_L2/38_g21_skystarry_R2", "solidwidth": "1280/1280/1280/1280", "solidheight": "720/720/720/720", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 60.0, "yFrom": 720.0, "yTo": 360.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個人躺在盛夏的草地上，看著一覽無餘的星空。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她知道，即使星星的位置看起來和昨天的並無不同，但其實它們一直在永不停歇地變化。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩顆現在相鄰的星星，即使被人們賦予意義，在千萬年後，也會變得無比遙遠，毫無瓜葛。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就和人與人之間的關係一樣。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天，她也沒有回來。"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在渺無人煙的小島，僅憑腦海中微弱的記憶，構建一個不可確信的夢。"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "囿於記憶的牢籠，如同人偶一般。"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執著與悲傷填充著身體，膨脹，膨脹。"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卻動彈不得。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始，我以為她只是突發奇想，去附近散步而已。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來，我從碼頭工人的口中得知，她那天獨自登上了離島的航船……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼不去找她呢？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的一天實在有過太多太多次，多到我不能確認它到底是否真實。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我已經想不起她的模樣，也不記得她的名字了。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許這就是我的歸宿……在這裡靜靜地等待。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "等待她的歸來，又或是我的死亡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "悲傷的源泉終有一天會乾涸，沒有更多的眼淚，便不會再哭泣了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這樣無人關心的角落，就是我最好的歸宿。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "“不行！”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 28.0, "delay": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#8$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#8$2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華小姐，你在哭，說明你還不想放棄，對吧？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是你想要的結局，對吧？！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "艾雅法拉", "content": "至少……"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "艾雅法拉", "content": "至少，應該站在她的面前，表達自己的想法吧。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#7$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#7$2"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能聽出來的話，她一定也能明白你的心意。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用盡全力吶喊，又怎麼能傳達給她呢？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連我都能聽到你的聲音，她肯定也可以的。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#7$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……可是你的聽力狀況，我不能留下你一個人——", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#7$2"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再怎麼說，我也是接受過羅德島訓練的幹員，你就放心吧。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們本來就是萍水相逢的兩個人，初華小姐，你已經為我做了很多事了。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該問問自己的內心——現在到底想要做什麼？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）我想找到她……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒什麼。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華小姐，我看得懂唇語喔。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "“看吧，你已無路可逃”", "x": 300.0, "y": 220.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“將逐漸虛弱的你，緊緊關住——”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“你知曉我渴望……”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“我渴望……我渴望……”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“我如此渴望著你……”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g5_siestaunbuiltland_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstprun", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "srun"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "srun", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當初華察覺到時，她已經在全力地奔跑了。"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她感到胸腔前所未有地炙熱，這種感覺甚至讓她有些頭暈目眩。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而最後的一絲理智，還在不斷地質問著她——"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "連名字都不記得，連面貌都想不起……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你又如何能在茫茫人海裡找到她的身影？", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我想見到她！", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，我都想再次見到她！", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的聲音先她一步，朝心中的方向飛去。"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而她，正奮力地朝自己聲音的方向奔去。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "srun", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子順利來到了別墅，這裡的一切都跟莫菲絲讓她看到的一模一樣。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華——", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一模一樣的格局、一模一樣的擺設……就連架子上的書都完全一樣。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地面上一塵不染，廚房裡擺滿了過量的餐具，還有一張能坐下十多人的長桌。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子無法想像初華一個人生活於此的場景。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然是做夢，那就把痛苦的部分丟得一乾二淨啊……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一定是她覺得，這裡對於你們兩人來說，都很重要吧。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就是這棟別墅的主人吧……初華小姐剛剛離開這裡。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她去哪裡了？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她終於認清了自己的內心，決定去找你了。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g3_islandharbor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要坐船嗎？", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我想買張離島的船票。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，那你要等一下哦，我還在等另一個乘客。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個小姐怎麼還沒回來呢……希望她已經找到人了。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，我可以等……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華說到一半，硬生生地將下半句話吞了回去，幸好船夫並沒有察覺她的異樣。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，夜晚海上浪大霧濃，這個時候出航很危險，我得為你們的安全著想啊！", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喏，你聽塔那邊發的訊號，那個傢伙在催我們走呢。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i05_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.15, "yScale": 1.15, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.15, "yScaleFrom": 1.15, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 15.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔上的那個人，他在揮舞旗子……", "name": "三角初華"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，那個老酒鬼就靠我每個月帶給他的啤酒續命。", "name": "熱心的船夫"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“一路平安，別忘記了——我的啤酒。”", "name": "熱心的船夫"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，忘記誰的東西，也不能忘記他的那箱美酒啊！", "name": "熱心的船夫"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船夫說完，一個箭步登上了船。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipwhistle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由海面吹來的風，將汽笛聲帶去小島的每一個地方。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看著這座寄託了美好和痛苦的小島，初華有太多話想傾訴。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……別忘記我。", "name": "三角初華"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "不可能忘記的吧。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們從小時候就一起在這裡生活。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我相信，我們一定會再次相見——", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_keeprunning", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "step", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華——！", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……呼……呼……咳咳咳……", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i05_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華——初華——！", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_harbor_busy", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子的聲音已經沙啞。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海浪一遍遍拍打著海岸，沒有回聲。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "返航的船已經駛離。"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，只留她一人獨守於此。"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g4_islandharbor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_strangeclap", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等待了無數個日夜的少女，終於決心啟程尋找自己的夥伴。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到卻在最後一刻錯過……嘖嘖嘖，好可惜喲。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老實說，我沒想到她會選擇離開。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我幫她預設的結局裡，她應該會忘掉關於你的一切，然後在這度過安逸無憂的一生。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過現在看來，我有點低估你對她的影響了。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得承認，這局我們平手。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜的是，以那艘航船的速度，她就快要遇到海難了。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為你們建造這整座島已經夠累了，難道還要我把整個泰拉打造出來，讓你們的苦情戲碼在整片大地上一遍遍地上演？", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船很快就要開到夢境的邊際了，然後她就會落入下一次的夢境。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一次次循環，一次次重置。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最終她會忘記你的存在。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，我要想辦法追上她——", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經沒有時間了。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子感到自己腳下一陣冰涼，不知何時，海水已經漫過腳踝。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大海與天空的連接處已經被陰雲籠罩，其中時不時閃爍著刺眼的光芒。"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華——！", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海水像瘋了一樣不斷地上漲，祥子感覺到有什麼正在將自己拖往深淵。"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華——等著我！", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g12_diving", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_underwtr", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "u"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "u", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幽暗，冰冷，窒息。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海水壓迫著鼓膜，殘存在胸腔中的氧氣漸漸稀薄，就和頭頂越來越微弱的光一樣。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "視線逐漸模糊，鹹苦的海水從無法緊閉的嘴中湧入，試圖侵占最後的意識。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就這樣，就這樣，一直下墜。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到海底，暗無天日之處。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "u", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“祥……”"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“祥……祥……”"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個聲音，正從無法辨認的方向靠近。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這裡是哪裡？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "是誰在叫我？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快……快……快醒醒……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "熟悉的聲音，許久未聞的聲音。"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冰冷潮濕的海底已經消失得無影無蹤，取而代之的是乾燥的地面，還有四處紛飛的沙塵。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰……", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i06", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "cg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子努力睜開雙眼，一縷淺色的頭髮映入眼簾。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "type": "cg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥，你還好嗎？", "name": "若葉睦"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……睦？", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我在。", "name": "若葉睦"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再簡單不過的一句話，卻讓祥子的眼淚奪眶而出。"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她確信不是飛沙的緣故，因為只有她自己知道，此刻她的內心有多麼無助。"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她已無暇顧及自己一開口便會哽咽，她只想抓住唯一的那根稻草。"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦……我……該怎麼辦……", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}